content: Liuqinwadang Museum, it should be closed recently, so if you have friends interested in this aspect, don't be empty.
The exhibition here is a multi-country Wadang in Asia, the exhibits are very artistic and historical value, really worth visiting.
located between the Bongeunsa Station and the Samsung Central station, Bongeun Park is a park that is rather small in size but has its distinct charm. The park also has a ‘meditation street’.
Every morning, I take a walk, and the clean forest road is meditating and walking is great. I look forward to autumn.
